org.hps.recon.ecal.cluster

Class LegacyClusterer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.recon.ecal.cluster.AbstractClusterer
      • org.hps.recon.ecal.cluster.LegacyClusterer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, Clusterer, ConditionsListener

    public class LegacyClusterer
extends AbstractClusterer

    This Driver creates clusters from a CalorimeterHit input collection.

    The clustering algorithm is implemented according to the description on pages 83 and 84 of the HPS Proposal document.
